de.rwth.i2.attestor.semantics.jimpleSemantics.jimple.statements.invoke

Class StaticInvokeHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rwth.i2.attestor.main.scene.SceneObject
      • de.rwth.i2.attestor.semantics.jimpleSemantics.jimple.statements.invoke.InvokeHelper
        • de.rwth.i2.attestor.semantics.jimpleSemantics.jimple.statements.invoke.StaticInvokeHelper

  • public class StaticInvokeHelper
extends InvokeHelper
    Prepares the heap for the invoke of a static method and cleans it afterwards.

    Call prepareHeap(input) for the heap that initializes the method call and cleanHeap( result ) on heaps that result from the execution of the abstract Method.

    Handles the evaluation of parameter expressions and stores them in the heap, by setting the corresponding intermediates.
    Cleans the heap after the execution of the method.
    Author:
    Hannah Arndt
